<h3 id="count"><a href="#count">count</a> {github(db/db_query_builder_driver.count)}</h3>
<p class="well">
	function counting number of records inside requested recordset.<br>
	Default parameter is: <code>$id = '*', $as_sql = false</code><br>
	If parameter <code>$as_sql = true</code> return simple sql command, else - return query result
</p>
<pre title="Example"><code>from('table')->count();</code></pre>

